        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1629",
        "content": "Seven of the judges said that was quite true, and mr Hampden was bound to pay: five of the judges said that was quite false, and mr Hampden was not bound to pay.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
